'''Ierians''' were [[Human/Legends|Humans]] from [[Ieria]]. The wealthier planet [[Andara/Legends|Andara]] was their rival. The Ierians did not enjoy indirect senatorial representation through Andara, and attempted an attack on Andara in [[26 BBY/Legends|26 BBY]].

